{"tid":28153,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"簡單取材既劇情片分享","createTime":"2016-12-07T18:29:12.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T19:34:59.000Z","uid":1103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e17e097e914e7583bcc729f0f7356551204f5a7a","tid":28153,"uid":1103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:29:12.000Z","msg":"1. Jagten (The Hunt) 狩獵<br />\n故事中男主角因為一件冇做過既事而搞到生活處處狼狽。<br />\n而原因只係以訛傳訛，大家都話係，所以件事就係真。<br />\n電影最後用幾個鏡頭諷刺現實世界群眾要攻擊一個人，就好似狩獵中要射倒一隻蕩失路既鹿咁簡單。<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.imdb.com/title/tt2106476/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.imdb.com%2Ftitle%2Ftt2106476%2F&d=FPzNj61AfF79le05kAvos2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=08ef458f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.imdb.com/title/tt2106476/</a>"},{"pid":"a743fe35d608497b6f328ac684d5f6b857c44180","tid":28153,"uid":1103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:33:50.000Z","msg":"2. Detachment 超脫<br />\n主角係一個背景悲哀既老師，不斷係唔同學校臨時任教。<br />\n因為佢既背景，佢對生活同自己漠不關心。<br />\n故事中，男主角當時身處既學校，係一間就要殺校既中學。無論老師定係學生，都對自己生命既追求一無所知，只係係制度下不斷feedback loop。<br />\n我覺得電影想表達人要做返自己，正如存在主義所講，Existence precedes excence。<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.imdb.com/title/tt1683526/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.imdb.com%2Ftitle%2Ftt1683526%2F&d=FPzNj61AfF79le05kAvos2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=ae579f62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.imdb.com/title/tt1683526/</a>"},{"pid":"53cbe7db05bc92c1529b974cb304e98af9adfb20","tid":28153,"uid":1103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:35:45.000Z","msg":"我會keep住更新，直到講晒呢排睇既電影。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f99e5a5c9767c9ace340dfc8dfa34ec09cd429ba","tid":28153,"uid":20641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T19:34:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}